data.description: Fantastic, well-maintained cape cod in East Deer Township. This home is move-in ready with plaster walls, arched doorways, newer furnace, water heater, roof, windows, electrical and upgraded bath. Trust believes there are hardwood floors under wall to wall carpet. Spacious bedrooms with decent size closets. Large, open, bright, dry basement with washer, dryer, toilet, shower, 2 extra storage rooms and a walkout. Enjoy peaceful views of the Allegheny River from your front porch. Great side and back lot big enough for gardening, small enough for easy maintenance. Quiet, dead end street. Convenient to mall and Route 28.
